title: Ep. 690 Economic Warning Signs?
description:
Summary:
In this episode I address the importance of combatting liberal identity politics and the warning signs on the horizons with regard to the economy. 
 
News Picks:
No, the Reagan tax cuts did not cause the deficits.
 
Is a trade war brewing? 
 
The liberals have now moved on “Christian privilege.”
 
Is artificial intelligence going to be watching you in the workplace?
 
Trump’s EPA pick makes a solid move for the auto industry.
 
Liberals love attacking inanimate statues.
